"use strict";(self.webpackChunkcasbin_website_v2=self.webpackChunkcasbin_website_v2||[]).push([[4918],{7527:n=>{n.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"/2021/08/19/apisix-casbin-authorization","metadata":{"permalink":"/tr/blog/2021/08/19/apisix-casbin-authorization","editUrl":"https://github.com/casbin/casbin-website-v2/edit/master/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2021-08-19-apisix-casbin-authorization.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2021-08-19-apisix-casbin-authorization.md","title":"APISIX\'te Casbin kullanarak yetkilendirme","description":"Giri\u015f","date":"2021-08-19T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"19 A\u011fustos 2021","tags":[],"readingTime":4.46,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Rushikesh Tote","title":"Casbin \xdcyesi","url":"http://github.com/rushitote","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/rushitote"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"APISIX\'te Casbin kullanarak yetkilendirme","author":"Rushikesh Tote","authorTitle":"Casbin \xdcyesi","authorURL":"http://github.com/rushitote","authorImageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/rushitote"},"nextItem":{"title":"Yang Luo - Google A\xe7\u0131k Kaynak E\u015f \xd6d\xfcl\xfc Kazanan\u0131","permalink":"/tr/blog/2020/04/21/google-award"}},"content":"## Giri\u015f\\n\\n[APISIX](https://apisix.apache.org/), Nginx ve etcd \xfczerine kurulu y\xfcksek performansl\u0131 ve \xf6l\xe7eklenebilir bir bulut yerel API a\u011f ge\xe7ididir. Apache Yaz\u0131l\u0131m Vakf\u0131 taraf\u0131ndan y\xfcr\xfct\xfclen a\xe7\u0131k kaynakl\u0131 bir projedir. APISIX\'in bu kadar iyi olmas\u0131n\u0131n yan\u0131 s\u0131ra, kimlik do\u011frulama, izleme, y\xf6nlendirme gibi \xf6zellikleri uygulamak i\xe7in kullan\u0131labilecek bir\xe7ok harika yerle\u015fik eklenti deste\u011fi bulunmaktad\u0131r. APISIX\'teki eklentilerin yeniden ba\u015flatmalar olmadan s\u0131cak y\xfcklenebilmesi, onu \xe7ok dinamik k\u0131lmaktad\u0131r.\\n\\nAncak APISIX kullan\u0131rken, uygulaman\u0131zda karma\u015f\u0131k yetkilendirme mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 eklemek isteyebilece\u011finiz senaryolar olabilir. \u0130\u015fte burada authz-casbin size yard\u0131mc\u0131 olabilir, authz-casbin, \xe7e\u015fitli eri\u015fim kontrol modellerine dayal\u0131 g\xfc\xe7l\xfc yetkilendirme sa\u011flayan [Lua Casbin](https://github.com/casbin/lua-casbin/) tabanl\u0131 bir APISIX eklentisidir. [Casbin](/), ACL, RBAC, ABAC gibi eri\u015fim kontrol modellerini destekleyen bir yetkilendirme k\xfct\xfcphanesidir. Ba\u015flang\u0131\xe7ta Go dilinde yaz\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olan Casbin, bir\xe7ok dilde port edilmi\u015ftir ve Lua Casbin, Casbin\'in Lua uygulamas\u0131d\u0131r. authz-casbin\'in geli\u015ftirilmesi, APISIX deposunda yetkilendirme i\xe7in yeni bir eklenti \xf6nerdi\u011fimizde ([#4674](https://github.com/apache/apisix/issues/4674)) \xe7ekirdek \xfcyelerin de onay vermesiyle ba\u015flad\u0131. Ve yararl\u0131 incelemeler sonucu baz\u0131 \xf6nemli de\u011fi\u015fiklikler ve iyile\u015ftirmeler yap\u0131ld\u0131ktan sonra, PR ([#4710](https://github.com/apache/apisix/pull/4710)) nihayet birle\u015ftirildi.\\n\\nBu blogda, authz-casbin eklentisini kullanarak APISIX\'te Rol Tabanl\u0131 Eri\u015fim Kontrol\xfc (RBAC) temelli bir yetkilendirme modelinin nas\u0131l uygulanabilece\u011fini g\xf6sterece\u011fiz.\\n\\n**NOT**: Casbin sadece yetkilendirme yapaca\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n kimlik do\u011frulamas\u0131 i\xe7in ba\u015fka bir eklenti veya \xf6zel bir i\u015f ak\u0131\u015f\u0131 kullanman\u0131z gerekecektir.\\n\\n## Model Olu\u015fturma\\n\\nEklenti, herhangi bir iste\u011fi yetkilendirmek i\xe7in \xfc\xe7 parametre kullan\u0131r - konu, nesne ve eylem. Burada, konu, kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131 ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131n de\u011feridir ve `[username: alice]` gibi bir \u015fey olabilir. Ard\u0131ndan, nesne eri\u015filmekte olan URL yolu ve eylem kullan\u0131lan istek y\xf6ntemidir.\\n\\nDiyelim ki `/`, `/res1` ve `/res2` yollar\u0131nda \xfc\xe7 kaynakla bir model olu\u015fturmak istiyoruz. Ve \u015f\xf6yle bir model istiyoruz:\\n\\n![resim](/img/blog/model.png)\\n\\nBu, \xf6rne\u011fin `jack` gibi t\xfcm kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n (`*`) anasayfas\u0131na (`/`) eri\u015febilece\u011fi anlam\u0131na gelir. Ve `alice` ve `bob` gibi `admin` izinlerine sahip kullan\u0131c\u0131lar t\xfcm sayfalara ve kaynaklara (\xf6rne\u011fin `res1` ve `res2`) eri\u015febilir. Ayr\u0131ca, admin izni olmayan kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n sadece `GET` istek y\xf6ntemini kullanmas\u0131n\u0131 k\u0131s\u0131tlayal\u0131m. Bu senaryo i\xe7in modeli \u015fu \u015fekilde tan\u0131mlayabiliriz:\\n\\n```ini\\n[request_definition]\\nr = sub, obj, act\\n\\n[policy_definition]\\np = sub, obj, act\\n\\n[role_definition]\\ng = _, _\\n\\n[policy_effect]\\ne = some(where (p.eft == allow))\\n\\n[matchers]\\nm = (g(r.sub, p.sub) || keyMatch(r.sub, p.sub)) && keyMatch(r.obj, p.obj) && keyMatch(r.act, p.act)\\n```\\n\\n## Politika olu\u015fturma\\n\\nYukar\u0131daki senaryodan, politika \u015fu \u015fekilde olacakt\u0131r:\\n\\n```csv\\np, *, /, GET\\np, admin, *, *\\ng, alice, admin\\ng, bob, admin\\n```\\n\\nModelden gelen e\u015fle\u015ftirici \u015fu anlama gelir:\\n\\n1. `(g(r.sub, p.sub) || keyMatch(r.sub, p.sub))`: \u0130ste\u011fin konusu, politikan\u0131n konusu olarak bir rol\xfc ta\u015f\u0131yor ya da iste\u011fin konusu, `keyMatch` i\xe7inde politikan\u0131n konusuyla e\u015fle\u015fiyor. `keyMatch`, Lua Casbin\'de yerle\u015fik bir fonksiyondur, fonksiyonun a\xe7\u0131klamas\u0131na ve daha faydal\u0131 olabilecek di\u011fer fonksiyonlara [buradan](https://github.com/casbin/lua-casbin/blob/master/src/util/BuiltInFunctions.lua) g\xf6z atabilirsiniz.\\n2. `keyMatch(r.obj, p.obj)`: \u0130ste\u011fin nesnesi, politikan\u0131n nesnesiyle e\u015fle\u015fiyor (burada URL yolu).\\n3. `keyMatch(r.act, p.act)`: \u0130ste\u011fin eylemi, politikan\u0131n eylemiyle e\u015fle\u015fiyor (burada HTTP istek metodu).\\n\\n## Eklentiyi rotada etkinle\u015ftirme\\n\\nModeli ve politikay\u0131 olu\u015fturduktan sonra, APISIX Admin API\'sini kullanarak bunu bir rotada etkinle\u015ftirebilirsiniz. Model ve politika dosyas\u0131 yollar\u0131n\u0131 kullanarak etkinle\u015ftirmek i\xe7in:\\n\\n```sh\\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:9080/apisix/admin/routes/1 -H \'X-API-KEY: edd1c9f034335f136f87ad84b625c8f1\' -X PUT -d \'\\n{\\n    \\"plugins\\": {\\n        \\"authz-casbin\\": {\\n            \\"model_path\\": \\"/path/to/model.conf\\",\\n            \\"policy_path\\": \\"/path/to/policy.csv\\",\\n            \\"username\\": \\"username\\"\\n        }\\n    },\\n    \\"upstream\\": {\\n        \\"nodes\\": {\\n            \\"127.0.0.1:1980\\": 1\\n        },\\n        \\"type\\": \\"roundrobin\\"\\n    },\\n    \\"uri\\": \\"/*\\"\\n}\'\\n```\\n\\nBurada, kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131 alan\u0131, konuyu iletece\u011finiz ba\u015fl\u0131k ad\u0131d\u0131r. \xd6rne\u011fin, kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131 ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 `user: alice` olarak iletecekseniz, `\\"username\\": \\"user\\"` kullan\u0131rs\u0131n\u0131z.\\n\\nDosyalar yerine model/politika metni kullanmak i\xe7in, `model` ve `policy` alanlar\u0131n\u0131 kullanabilirsiniz:\\n\\n```sh\\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:9080/apisix/admin/routes/1 -H \'X-API-KEY: edd1c9f034335f136f87ad84b625c8f1\' -X PUT -d \'\\n{\\n    \\"plugins\\": {\\n        \\"authz-casbin\\": {\\n            \\"model\\": \\"[request_definition]\\n            r = sub, obj, act\\n\\n            [policy_definition]\\n            p = sub, obj, act\\n\\n            [role_definition]\\n            g = _, _\\n\\n            [policy_effect]\\n            e = some(where (p.eft == allow))\\n\\n            [matchers]\\n            m = (g(r.sub, p.sub) || keyMatch(r.sub, p.sub)) && keyMatch(r.obj, p.obj) && keyMatch(r.act, p.act)\\",\\n\\n            \\"policy\\": \\"p, *, /, GET\\n            p, admin, *, *\\n            g, alice, admin\\n            g, bob, admin\\",\\n\\n            \\"username\\": \\"username\\"\\n        }\\n    },\\n    \\"upstream\\": {\\n        \\"nodes\\": {\\n            \\"127.0.0.1:1980\\": 1\\n        },\\n        \\"type\\": \\"roundrobin\\"\\n    },\\n    \\"uri\\": \\"/*\\"\\n}\'\\n```\\n\\n## Eklentiyi global bir model/politika kullanarak etkinle\u015ftirme\\n\\nBirden fazla rotada tek bir model ve politika yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131 kullanmak isteyebilece\u011finiz durumlar olabilir. Bunu, \xf6ncelikle model ve politika yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131 eklentinin meta verilerine eklemek i\xe7in bir `PUT` iste\u011fi g\xf6ndererek yapabilirsiniz:\\n\\n```sh\\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:9080/apisix/admin/plugin_metadata/authz-casbin -H \'X-API-KEY: edd1c9f034335f136f87ad84b625c8f1\' -i -X PUT -d \'\\n{\\n\\"model\\": \\"[request_definition]\\nr = sub, obj, act\\n\\n[policy_definition]\\np = sub, obj, act\\n\\n[role_definition]\\ng = _, _\\n\\n[policy_effect]\\ne = some(where (p.eft == allow))\\n\\n[matchers]\\nm = (g(r.sub, p.sub) || keyMatch(r.sub, p.sub)) && keyMatch(r.obj, p.obj) && keyMatch(r.act, p.act)\\",\\n\\n\\"policy\\": \\"p, *, /, GET\\np, admin, *, *\\ng, alice, admin\\ng, bob, admin\\"\\n}\'\\n```\\n\\nVe sonra ayn\u0131 yap\u0131land\u0131rmay\u0131 baz\u0131 rotalarda etkinle\u015ftirmek i\xe7in, Admin API\'sini kullanarak bir istek g\xf6nderin:\\n\\n```sh\\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:9080/apisix/admin/routes/1 -H \'X-API-KEY: edd1c9f034335f136f87ad84b625c8f1\' -X PUT -d \'\\n{\\n    \\"plugins\\": {\\n        \\"authz-casbin\\": {\\n            \\"username\\": \\"username\\"\\n        }\\n    },\\n    \\"upstream\\": {\\n        \\"nodes\\": {\\n            \\"127.0.0.1:1980\\": 1\\n        },\\n        \\"type\\": \\"roundrobin\\"\\n    },\\n    \\"uri\\": \\"/route1/*\\"\\n}\'\\n```\\n\\nBu, eklenti meta veri yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131 rotaya ekleyecektir. Eklenti meta veri yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131, g\xfcncellenmi\u015f model ve politika yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131 ile iste\u011fi yeniden g\xf6ndererek kolayca g\xfcncelleyebilirsiniz, eklenti otomatik olarak eklenti meta verisini kullanan t\xfcm rotalar\u0131 g\xfcncelleyecektir.\\n\\n## Kullan\u0131m Senaryolar\u0131\\n\\n- Bu eklentinin birincil kullan\u0131m senaryosu, API\'lerinizde yetkilendirmeyi uygulamak olacakt\u0131r. Bu eklentiyi, yetkilendirme modeliniz ve politika yap\u0131land\u0131rman\u0131zla kullanmakta oldu\u011funuz herhangi bir API rotas\u0131na kolayca ekleyebilirsiniz.\\n- T\xfcm API\'leriniz i\xe7in tek bir yetkilendirme modeline sahip olmak istiyorsan\u0131z, global model/politika y\xf6ntemini kullanabilirsiniz. Bu, politika g\xfcncellemesini t\xfcm rotalar i\xe7in kolayla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r, \xe7\xfcnk\xfc sadece etcd\'deki meta verileri g\xfcncellemeniz yeterlidir.\\n- E\u011fer her farkl\u0131 rotaya farkl\u0131 bir model kullanmak istiyorsan\u0131z, rota y\xf6ntemini kullanabilirsiniz. Bu, farkl\u0131 API rotalar\u0131n\u0131n farkl\u0131 kullan\u0131c\u0131 izinlerine sahip oldu\u011funda yard\u0131mc\u0131 olur. Ayr\u0131ca, daha b\xfcy\xfck politikalarla u\u011fra\u015f\u0131rken bunu kullanabilirsiniz, \xe7\xfcnk\xfc bu, yetkilendirmeyi birden \xe7ok rota filtrelendi\u011finde daha h\u0131zl\u0131 yapacakt\u0131r."},{"id":"/2020/04/21/google-award","metadata":{"permalink":"/tr/blog/2020/04/21/google-award","editUrl":"https://github.com/casbin/casbin-website-v2/edit/master/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2020-04-21-google-award.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2020-04-21-google-award.md","title":"Yang Luo - Google A\xe7\u0131k Kaynak E\u015f \xd6d\xfcl\xfc Kazanan\u0131","description":"Bug\xfcn, Casbin\'in kurucusunun, Yang Luo\'nun 2019 Q3\'te Casbin, Npcap ve Nmap \xfczerindeki \xe7al\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131 nedeniyle \\"Google A\xe7\u0131k Kaynak E\u015f \xd6d\xfcl\xfc kazananlar\u0131\\" aras\u0131nda yer ald\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 duyurmaktan mutluluk duyuyoruz.","date":"2020-04-21T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"21 Nisan 2020","tags":[],"readingTime":0.635,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Casbin","title":"Resmi Hesap","url":"http://github.com/casbin","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/casbin"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Yang Luo - Google A\xe7\u0131k Kaynak E\u015f \xd6d\xfcl\xfc Kazanan\u0131","author":"Casbin","authorTitle":"Resmi Hesap","authorURL":"http://github.com/casbin","authorImageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/casbin"},"prevItem":{"title":"APISIX\'te Casbin kullanarak yetkilendirme","permalink":"/tr/blog/2021/08/19/apisix-casbin-authorization"},"nextItem":{"title":"Belgelerimizi Yeniden D\xfczenleme","permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/09/23/new-website"}},"content":"Bug\xfcn, Casbin\'in kurucusunun, [Yang Luo](https://github.com/hsluoyz)\'nun 2019 Q3\'te [Casbin](/), [Npcap](https://nmap.org/npcap/) ve [Nmap](https://nmap.org/) \xfczerindeki \xe7al\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131 nedeniyle \\"Google A\xe7\u0131k Kaynak E\u015f \xd6d\xfcl\xfc kazananlar\u0131\\" aras\u0131nda yer ald\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 duyurmaktan mutluluk duyuyoruz.\\n\\n![ospb](https://hsluoyz.github.io/download/Open%20Source%20Peer%20Bonus%20Q3%202019%20-%20Yang%20Luo%20-%20OSPB%20Award%20Letter.png)\\n\\n> Orijinal \xf6d\xfcl mektubu [buradan](https://github.com/hsluoyz/hsluoyz.github.io/blob/master/download/Open%20Source%20Peer%20Bonus%20Q3%202019%20-%20Yang%20Luo%20-%20OSPB%20Award%20Letter.pdf) eri\u015filebilir.\\n\\n[Google Open Source Peer Bonus](https://opensource.google.com/docs/growing/peer-bonus/) program\u0131 \u015fu \u015fekilde a\xe7\u0131klanmaktad\u0131r:\\n\\n> _Bir Google Peer Bonus, \xf6zellikle a\u015fan bir Google \xe7al\u0131\u015fan\u0131n\u0131 tan\u0131tmak i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131rken, bir Open Source Peer Bonus, a\xe7\u0131k kaynakl\u0131 projelere ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc katk\u0131larda bulunan d\u0131\u015f ki\u015fileri tan\u0131mak i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r._\\n\\n2019 y\u0131l\u0131 kazananlar\u0131 i\xe7in [duyurusu](https://opensource.googleblog.com/2020/01/announcing-2019-second-cycle-google.html) \u015fu adreste mevcuttur:\\n\\n> https://opensource.googleblog.com/2020/01/announcing-2019-second-cycle-google.html\\n\\nYang ve Casbin, Git, TensorFlow, V8, CPython, LLVM, Apache projeleri, Angular veya Jenkins gibi a\xe7\u0131k kaynak geli\u015ftiricileri ve projeleri aras\u0131nda \xf6nemli bir etkiye sahip olarak listelenmi\u015ftir.\\n\\nCasbin\'in a\xe7\u0131k kaynak ve bulut g\xfcvenli\u011fi i\xe7in yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 katk\u0131lar\u0131 bu \u015fekilde tan\u0131d\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6rmekten memnuniyet duyuyoruz!\\n\\n_Casbin ile u\xe7u\u015f i\xe7in te\u015fekk\xfcrler!_"},{"id":"/2018/09/23/new-website","metadata":{"permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/09/23/new-website","editUrl":"https://github.com/casbin/casbin-website-v2/edit/master/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2018-09-23-new-website.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2018-09-23-new-website.md","title":"Belgelerimizi Yeniden D\xfczenleme","description":"Bug\xfcn, Casbin\'in dok\xfcmantasyonunu GitHub Wiki\'den bu web sitesinin Docs b\xf6l\xfcm\xfcne ta\u015f\u0131d\u0131k, Docusaurus, daha iyi Markdown stilleri, tam metin arama, s\xfcr\xfcm olu\u015fturma, \xe7eviri gibi bir\xe7ok harika \xf6zelli\u011fi sunar.","date":"2018-09-23T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"23 Eyl\xfcl 2018","tags":[],"readingTime":0.24,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Yang Luo","title":"Casbin\'in Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131","url":"http://github.com/hsluoyz","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/hsluoyz"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Belgelerimizi Yeniden D\xfczenleme","author":"Yang Luo","authorTitle":"Casbin\'in Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131","authorURL":"http://github.com/hsluoyz","authorImageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/hsluoyz"},"prevItem":{"title":"Yang Luo - Google A\xe7\u0131k Kaynak E\u015f \xd6d\xfcl\xfc Kazanan\u0131","permalink":"/tr/blog/2020/04/21/google-award"},"nextItem":{"title":"node-Casbin: Casbin Ailesinin Yeni \xdcyesi","permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/08/27/node-casbin"}},"content":"Bug\xfcn, Casbin\'in dok\xfcmantasyonunu GitHub Wiki\'den bu web sitesinin `Docs` b\xf6l\xfcm\xfcne ta\u015f\u0131d\u0131k, Docusaurus, daha iyi Markdown stilleri, tam metin arama, s\xfcr\xfcm olu\u015fturma, \xe7eviri gibi bir\xe7ok harika \xf6zelli\u011fi sunar.\\n\\nDok\xfcmantasyon hen\xfcz m\xfckemmel de\u011fil ve h\xe2l\xe2 ayarlama gerektiriyor. Kaynak kodu GitHub\'da bar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131l\u0131yor: https://github.com/casbin/casbin-website-v2 .\\n\\nHer t\xfcrl\xfc katk\u0131 veya \xf6neri ho\u015f geldiniz!"},{"id":"/2018/08/27/node-casbin","metadata":{"permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/08/27/node-casbin","editUrl":"https://github.com/casbin/casbin-website-v2/edit/master/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2018-08-27-node-casbin.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2018-08-27-node-casbin.md","title":"node-Casbin: Casbin Ailesinin Yeni \xdcyesi","description":"Bug\xfcn, Casbin\'i Node.js\'ye ba\u015far\u0131yla ta\u015f\u0131d\u0131k, ad\u0131:","date":"2018-08-27T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"27 A\u011fustos 2018","tags":[],"readingTime":0.185,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Zixuan Liu","title":"Casbin Bak\u0131mc\u0131s\u0131","url":"http://github.com/nodece","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/nodece"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"node-Casbin: Casbin Ailesinin Yeni \xdcyesi","author":"Zixuan Liu","authorTitle":"Casbin Bak\u0131mc\u0131s\u0131","authorURL":"http://github.com/nodece","authorImageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/nodece"},"prevItem":{"title":"Belgelerimizi Yeniden D\xfczenleme","permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/09/23/new-website"},"nextItem":{"title":"Casbin Sunucusu Ba\u015flat\u0131ld\u0131!","permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/08/07/launching-casbin-server"}},"content":"Bug\xfcn, Casbin\'i Node.js\'ye ba\u015far\u0131yla ta\u015f\u0131d\u0131k, ad\u0131:\\n\\n**node-Casbin** Casbin\'in di\u011fer uygulamalar\u0131yla benzer kullan\u0131m\u0131 ve API\'ye sahiptir. Express, Koa2 ve Egg.js i\xe7in ara yaz\u0131l\u0131mlar kullan\u0131ma haz\u0131rd\u0131r. Sequelize i\xe7in depolama adapt\xf6r\xfc de haz\u0131rland\u0131.\\n\\nUmar\u0131m ihtiya\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 iyi kar\u015f\u0131lar :)\\n\\nGitHub: https://github.com/casbin/node-casbin"},{"id":"/2018/08/07/launching-casbin-server","metadata":{"permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/08/07/launching-casbin-server","editUrl":"https://github.com/casbin/casbin-website-v2/edit/master/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2018-08-07-launching-casbin-server.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2018-08-07-launching-casbin-server.md","title":"Casbin Sunucusu Ba\u015flat\u0131ld\u0131!","description":"Baz\u0131 m\xfc\u015fterilerimiz, Casbin\'in bir k\xfct\xfcphane yerine bir hizmet olarak kullan\u0131l\u0131p kullan\u0131lamayaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 soruyor. Cevap EVET. Bug\xfcn, Eri\u015fim Kontrol\xfc Olarak Hizmet i\xe7in somut bir \xe7\xf6z\xfcm olarak Casbin Server projemizi ba\u015flatt\u0131k.","date":"2018-08-07T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"7 A\u011fustos 2018","tags":[],"readingTime":0.57,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Helong Zhang","title":"Casbin Bak\u0131m\u0131","url":"http://github.com/BetaCat0","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/BetaCat0"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Casbin Sunucusu Ba\u015flat\u0131ld\u0131!","author":"Helong Zhang","authorTitle":"Casbin Bak\u0131m\u0131","authorURL":"http://github.com/BetaCat0","authorImageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/BetaCat0"},"prevItem":{"title":"node-Casbin: Casbin Ailesinin Yeni \xdcyesi","permalink":"/tr/blog/2018/08/27/node-casbin"}},"content":"Baz\u0131 m\xfc\u015fterilerimiz, Casbin\'in bir k\xfct\xfcphane yerine bir hizmet olarak kullan\u0131l\u0131p kullan\u0131lamayaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 soruyor. Cevap **EVET**. Bug\xfcn, **Eri\u015fim Kontrol\xfc Olarak Hizmet** i\xe7in somut bir \xe7\xf6z\xfcm olarak [Casbin Server](https://github.com/casbin/casbin-server) projemizi ba\u015flatt\u0131k.\\n\\n**Casbin Server**, \xe7ekirdek ekibimiz taraf\u0131ndan aktif olarak geli\u015ftirilmektedir. \xc7e\u015fitli \xf6zelliklere sahiptir:\\n\\n- Sadece Golang ile geli\u015ftirilmi\u015ftir.\\n- Binlerce Casbin \xf6rne\u011fini y\xf6netebilir, b\xf6ylece politikalar\u0131n uygulanmas\u0131 mant\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 birden fazla hizmetten tek bir Casbin Server\'a ta\u015f\u0131yabilirsiniz.\\n- **gRPC**, Casbin Server ile ileti\u015fim kurmak i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r. Yak\u0131n gelecekte **RESTful** deste\u011fini de eklemeyi d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcyoruz.\\n- Geli\u015ftirici olmayan y\xf6neticilerin Casbin \xf6rnekleri, modeller, politikalar\u0131n depolanmas\u0131 ve y\xfck dengeleme gibi t\xfcm detaylar\u0131 y\xf6netmeleri i\xe7in kullan\u0131\u015fl\u0131 bir web y\xf6netici portal\u0131 sa\u011flanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.\\n\\n\\n\\nKaynak kodu GitHub\'da bar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r: https://github.com/casbin/casbin-server\\n\\nHerhangi bir sorun veya \xe7ekme iste\u011fi ho\u015f geldiniz :)"}]}')}}]);